The '''Verpine power lance''' was the primary weapon of the [[clone lancer trooper]]s of the [[Lancer Battalion]] of the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]]. The power lance was specially designed for [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] operating [[105-K lancer bike]]s.

